69
00:03:23.102 --> 00:03:24.669
No one's been in or out
since the power went down.

70
00:03:24.721 --> 00:03:26.138
Morgan said they were
coming here. right?

71
00:03:26.189 --> 00:03:27.839
And he was a lot
closer than any of us.

72
00:03:27.890 --> 00:03:29.507
Something
must have changed.

73
00:03:29.559 --> 00:03:30.642
The cells are down.

74
00:03:30.693 --> 00:03:31.943
Now how the hell
do you find them?

75
00:03:32.011 --> 00:03:33.528
What would cause Morgan
to change his mind like that

76
00:03:33.613 --> 00:03:35.030
when he knows
he can't tell us?

77
00:03:35.114 --> 00:03:36.648
The unsub had Spicer's
sister and daughter.

78
00:03:36.699 --> 00:03:38.183
Morgan knew he didn't
have a lot of time.

79
00:03:38.234 --> 00:03:39.651
So his first guess
had to be right.

80
00:03:39.719 --> 00:03:41.820
The unsub
attacked Spicer

81
00:03:41.871 --> 00:03:43.572
