through his family.

82
00:03:43.656 --> 00:03:45.290
How long has Spicer's
sister lived here?

83
00:03:45.357 --> 00:03:46.408
6-7 months.

84
00:03:46.492 --> 00:03:47.826
Well. that's why
they didn't come here.

85
00:03:47.877 --> 00:03:49.327
If the unsub
wants to hurt Spicer.

86
00:03:49.378 --> 00:03:50.962
