that means something to him.

87
00:03:51.030 --> 00:03:53.865
Morgan must have realized
the same thing.

88
00:03:53.916 --> 00:03:56.218
The unsub and Spicer
do share one place in common.

89
00:03:56.302 --> 00:03:58.053
Santa Monica.
Where he killed his parents.

90
00:03:58.137 --> 00:03:59.671
Let's go.

91
00:03:59.722 --> 00:04:01.389
This is Kurzbard
in major crimes.

92
00:04:01.474 --> 00:04:02.974
I need a priority response.

93
00:04:06.529 --> 00:04:07.479
Uhh!

94
00:04:07.546 --> 00:04:09.648
Kristin.

95
00:04:09.715 --> 00:04:10.649
Kristin.

96
00:04:10.716 --> 00:04:11.900
Kristin.

97
00:04:11.984 --> 00:04:13.935
Ohh...

98
00:04:15.188 --> 00:04:16.721
Kristin.

99
00:04:16.773 --> 00:04:19.107
It's getting harder
to breathe.

100
00:04:19.192 --> 00:04:22.144
Just try to slow your breathing.
Just slow everything down.

101
00:04:22.211 --> 00:04:25.464
We have to get her back.

102
00:04:25.531 --> 00:04:27.732
She's just a baby.

103
00:04:29.085 --> 00:04:30.068
Look at me.

104
00:04:30.119 --> 00:04:32.921
Kristin. look at me.
I need you to tell me

105
00:04:33.005 --> 00:04:35.540
