bring you here?

126
00:05:30.596 --> 00:05:33.431
In an RV.

127
00:05:34.851 --> 00:05:36.968
An old...

128
00:05:37.019 --> 00:05:40.471
Filthy RV.

129
00:05:50.449 --> 00:05:52.167
