130
00:05:57.790 --> 00:05:59.841
Ellie?

131
00:06:02.328 --> 00:06:03.595
Don't worry.

132
00:06:03.662 --> 00:06:05.847
You'll get used to it.

133
00:06:14.907 --> 00:06:17.893
You let me get away
on purpose. didn't you?

134
00:06:17.977 --> 00:06:20.729
So that they'd open
their door.

135
00:06:29.288 --> 00:06:32.073
We're gonna make
a great team.

136
