Good.

185
00:09:11.598 --> 00:09:12.798
I was just--

186
00:09:12.849 --> 00:09:13.849
it's not you.

187
00:09:17.020 --> 00:09:19.137
Between the blackout
and the prince of darkness

188
00:09:19.189 --> 00:09:21.924
running around out there.
be advised to lock your...

189
