197
00:09:37.624 --> 00:09:38.957
Ok. I got it.

198
00:09:39.009 --> 00:09:40.459
Put the mask on.
He listens to the radio.

199
00:09:40.510 --> 00:09:41.877
Something else.

200
00:09:41.961 --> 00:09:44.380
The other agent--
you have to tell him.

201
00:09:44.464 --> 00:09:46.465
I made him promise...

202
00:09:46.516 --> 00:09:47.466
