217
00:10:12.375 --> 00:10:16.245
You know. she really needs
to be more professional sometimes.

218
00:10:16.329 --> 00:10:18.464
She gets the job done
every time.

219
00:10:20.333 --> 00:10:22.251
I told him. Hotch.

220
00:10:22.318 --> 00:10:24.753
I told him that we
should wait for backup.

221
00:10:24.838 --> 00:10:26.438
but he wouldn't
listen to me.

222
00:10:26.506 --> 00:10:27.923
We split up and he
headed around back

223
00:10:28.007 --> 00:10:29.224
