244
00:11:20.360 --> 00:11:21.927
...New permits.
which provide a sense

245
00:11:21.978 --> 00:11:24.279
of future home
construction. fell 3.5...

246
00:11:26.282 --> 00:11:28.433
We're not a team.

247
00:11:28.485 --> 00:11:31.269
You got us in.

248
00:11:31.321 --> 00:11:34.105
We did it together.

249
00:11:34.157 --> 00:11:37.442
But I--I didn't know.

250
00:11:37.494 --> 00:11:40.662
And if I didn't know.
we aren't a team.

251
00:11:40.747 --> 00:11:42.548
Yet.

252
00:11:46.169 --> 00:11:48.170
Why do you
have to kill people?

253
00:11:50.507 --> 00:11:53.308
My dad says people who hurt
other people are cowards.

254
00:11:53.393 --> 00:11:56.261
that they never hurt somebody
who can protect themselves.

255
00:11:56.312 --> 00:11:58.647
So how would he explain

256
00:11:58.731 --> 00:12:01.132
