820
00:41:26.329 --> 00:41:29.247
♪ who by water ♪

821
00:41:29.332 --> 00:41:32.918
♪ who in sunshine ♪

822
00:41:33.002 --> 00:41:36.288
♪ who in the nighttime... ♪

823
00:41:36.372 --> 00:41:39.073
A family is a place
where minds

824
00:41:39.125 --> 00:41:40.842
"come in contact
with one another.

825
00:41:40.910 --> 00:41:42.761
"If these minds
love one another.

826
00:41:42.845 --> 00:41:46.214
"the home will be as beautiful
as a flower garden.

827
00:41:46.265 --> 00:41:49.718
"But if these minds get out
of harmony with one another.

828
00:41:49.769 --> 00:41:52.921
it is like a storm that plays havoc
with the garden."

829
00:41:52.972 --> 00:41:53.955
The Buddha.

830
