♪ who by powder ♪

834
00:42:09.972 --> 00:42:13.992
♪ who for his creed ♪

835
00:42:14.076 --> 00:42:16.278
♪ who for his hunger ♪

836
00:42:16.329 --> 00:42:22.167
♪ and who shall I say ♪

837
00:42:22.251 --> 00:42:24.485
♪ is calling? ♪

838
00:42:28.508 --> 00:42:32.043
♪ and who by brave assent ♪

839
00:42:32.128 --> 00:42:35.663
♪ who by accident ♪

840
00:42:35.715 --> 00:42:38.934
♪ who in solitude ♪

841
00:42:39.001 --> 00:42:41.353
♪ who in this mirror ♪

842
00:42:41.437 --> 00:42:44.672
