843
00:42:44.724 --> 00:42:47.559
♪ who by his own hand ♪

844
00:42:47.627 --> 00:42:50.529
♪ who in mortal chains ♪

845
00:42:50.613 --> 00:42:53.398
♪ who in power ♪

846
00:42:53.482 --> 00:42:56.234
♪ and who ♪

847
